{"tid":2327221,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳因阻習近平「龍脈」北京香堂遭強拆　紅色詩人後代抗拆被捕","createTime":"2020-12-16T02:26:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T06:07:46.000Z","uid":184679,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"1d42690c79adab41b25ad4700d41b7fc865a3d56","tid":2327221,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T02:26:56.000Z","msg":"北京昌平香堂村小產權房強遷正式啟動，當局派過千警力維穩嚴防衝突升級，抗拆業主、紅色詩人郭小川的女兒已遭拘留，物業遭停水停電的中國政法大學教授也被迫絕食抗議。流亡美國的中共中央黨校前教授蔡霞曝習近平迷信風水，認為香堂壓住「龍脈」，公檢法聯手全力配合拆遷工作。在本台獲得的視頻中，一名地方官員透露拆遷「理由涉密」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www-rfa-org.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/demolish-12152020104633.html/@@images/image/social_media\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww-rfa-org.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Fdemolish-12152020104633.html%2F%40%40images%2Fimage%2Fsocial_media&h=3ecb0c0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/demolish-12152020104633.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Fdemolish-12152020104633.html&d=P3odlOe4J5oN5vIqyIzMUwoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=4622fafd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/demolish-12152020104633.html</a>"},{"pid":"891ab40fa5d7630bda16c02b2393fc0c7cdec3b4","tid":2327221,"uid":152476,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T02:28:21.000Z","msg":"戰狼包括對自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e7198dc3cfa32444eddcc5641e1f10b4745d5fe","tid":2327221,"uid":7484,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T02:31:40.000Z","msg":"唔斷龍脈 點加速 總加速師<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e4b4ceb99dbc6499d8b76eef6953e835e4a964b","tid":2327221,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4